      "content": {
        "howWeMet": {
          "title": "How We Met",
          "story": "Two years ago, in the midst of a demanding work schedule that left little time for anything else, I decided to break free and support some friends at their hangout show....",
          "detail-story": [
            "## A Crisp White Shirt and a Sweet, Firm Voice",
            "",
            "Two years ago, in the midst of a demanding work schedule that left little time for anything else, I decided to break free and support some friends at their hangout show. My only goal was to have some much-needed fun ‚Äì and boy, did I.",
            "",
            "It was there, across the room, that my eyes landed on him. He was handsome, quiet, and incredibly composed. But what truly caught my attention was his shirt ‚Äì it was a pristine, *crisp white* that seemed to glow, as immaculate as a white dove. As someone who appreciates clean white clothes, I was instantly intrigued. Then he spoke, and his voice, though firm and undeniably *masculine and sexy*, was also surprisingly soft and sweet.",
            "",
            "I caught him looking at me from across the room, and I won't lie, his gaze felt different. Even from that distance, I had a powerful feeling that he was *the one*. Yet, when the night ended, I left without saying a single word to him.",
            "",
            "---",
            "",
            "## The Melody That Brought Us Together",
            "",
            "The following month, my friends invited me out again, and this time, fate intervened. I finally got to speak to Adefemi, the man from across the room, one-on-one. We quickly discovered a shared passion for *music*, realizing the potential for us to collaborate as music ministers. Time was against us that night, as it was getting late, but we exchanged numbers, a silent promise of future conversations.",
            "",
            "And the rest, as they say, is history. Or perhaps it's more accurate to say, that's what brought us here, to this very day."
          ],
          "date": "2020",
          "location": "Lagos, Nigeria"
        },
        "proposal": {
          "title": "The Proposal",
          "story": "The moment that changed everything...",
